extendedInfo.description: ** Note this app IS NOT A STANDALONE! This skin requires GO Keyboard (Free on Market) or Ultra KeyboardMatch your keyboard with* Dark Phone GO SMS: http://bit.ly/HqmUc3* Dark Phone GO Contacts: http://bit.ly/LU4pPxFeatures* Optional custom font (see below to activate font)* Crisp graphics* Unique glow effect on letters* Activate through GO Keyboard settings!Install* Select done, return to GO Keyboard's Settings (hold 123 on Keyboard), and select the Dark Phone skin from the list of available skins.Activate the font* Go into GO Keyboard Settings, Advanced Setting, Font setting, Scan fonts.
